column5: This was featured on MSN's homepage today and thought Id post to see if any of the Nippissing locals saw it while surfing today  Island
I didn't see that but I did see this; Kayaking on grass goes badly  http://video.ca.msn.com/watch/video/kayaking-the-grass-goes-wrong/2jsjyc9a?from=en-ca-hpquad
What a steal but that Island does not look like 2 acres. And I think that may be native territory.  Would love to own that cottage!
Poor dude. Hope he is alright.
something tells me the guy in the Kayak said "her, hold my beer and watch this" just before the camera started to record...
wow if thats 2 acres ... I live on a farm !!!!!
I'd buy the 45 acre Island that's for sale, with 2 cabins and an airstip, on the Ottawa River first....
I've been looking at private islands for couple years now.. fun site to show friends
